---
import { Code, Lightbulb, Award } from '@lucide/astro';
---

<section 
  id="about" 
  class="snap-start min-h-screen py-20 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-32 text-gray-100 flex flex-col justify-center"
>
  <h2 
    class="text-4xl font-bold mb-10 inline-block pb-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-200 via-orange-300 to-amber-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent border-b-4 border-gradient-to-r animate-fade-in"
  >
    About Me
  </h2>

  <p class="text-lg max-w-3xl mb-12 leading-relaxed text-gray-300 animate-fade-up">
    Hi, Iâ€™m Borja, a Full Stack Developer with a passion for creating innovative and efficient digital solutions. With expertise in both frontend and backend technologies, I specialize in crafting seamless user experiences and robust application architectures.
  </p>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 max-w-5xl">
    
    <!-- What I Do -->
    <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <Code class="text-[#02fd9a]" size={28} />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What I Do</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-200">
        <li><strong>Frontend Development:</strong> Experienced in building modern and dynamic interfaces with React.js and Angular, paying close attention to user experience and following best practices in HTML, CSS, and modern JavaScript.</li>
        <li><strong>Backend Development:</strong> Skilled in developing robust and scalable applications with Django, implementing efficient and secure RESTful APIs to seamlessly connect frontend and backend.</li>
        <li><strong>Database Management:</strong> Proficient in managing and optimizing relational databases like MySQL and non-relational databases like MongoDB, ensuring performance, security, and data integrity.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- My Approach -->
    <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <Lightbulb class="text-[#02fd9a]" size={28} />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">My Approach</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-200 leading-relaxed">
        I thrive on solving complex problems through clean code and creative solutions. Whether working independently or as part of a team, I aim to deliver high-quality results that exceed expectations.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Choose Me -->
    <div class="bg-white/5 p-6 rounded-2xl hover:scale-105 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-300 shadow-md">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <Award class="text-[#02fd9a]" size={28} />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Why Choose Me?</h3>
      </div>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-200">
        <li>Passionate about learning and adopting the latest technologies.</li>
        <li>Dedicated to delivering on time and at high standards.</li>
        <li>Focused on creating impactful digital experiences.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
